atītair buddhair yā bhāṣitā anāgatāś ca ye samyaksaṃbuddhā hi yasmād yāṃ bhāṣiṣyante punaḥ | pratyutpannāś ca buddhā bhagavanto bhāṣante yāṃ nāmasaṃgītiṃ punar apīti || pratyutpannāś ca saṃbuddhā yāṃ bhāṣante punaḥ punaḥ ||

<commentary>māyājāletyādi | asmin māyājālamahātantre 'meyair mahāvajradharair mahāmantradhāribhir hṛṣtair yā saṃpragīyate tāṃ ||</commentary>

ahaṃ caināṃ dhārayiṣyāmy ā niryāṇād nirvāṇaṃ yāvat | kiṃbhūto dṛḍhāśayaḥ | ḍṛḍho 'vicala āśayo 'bhiprāyo yasyāsau dṛḍhāśaya iti |
